txt.en: Speak to Stálskeg Ironbeard to be given a small token of his esteem for your assistance.
Stálskeg Ironbeard has requested your aid in securing a foothold outside of Gundabad for the Gabil'akkâ, the Unified Army of Dwarves.

Stálskeg Ironbeard has requested your aid in securing a foothold outside of Gundabad for the Gabil'akkâ, the Unified Army of Dwarves. He has enlisted Hlóthi to gather several ongoing tasks that need to be completed throughout the area.
The War Effort: A Great Leap (Weekly)

'We must secure a foothold outside of Gundabad for the Gabil'akkâ, the Unified Army of Dwarves.\n\n'Hlóthi has asked that you accomplish several tasks to aid in this effort. If you are able to complete several tasks for him this week, we will be able to reward your accomplishments.'
Your assistance has truly assisted the Gabil'akkâ in its attempt to rescue our fallen homeland.
